===Noun===
''' lymphocyte ''' (''plural'' ''' lymphocytes ''')
# {{cytology}} A type of [[white blood cell]] or [[leukocyte]] that occurs in two forms; B-lymphocytes, which produce [[antibody|antibodies]] in the humoral immune response, and T-lymphocytes, which participates in the cell-mediated immune response.

